as dijagnosticiran koronavirus: Prvi slu\u010daj zaraze u Bu\u017eimu |url=https://www.oslobodjenje.ba/vijesti/bih/ko-su-osobe-iz-usk-kojima-je-danas-dijagnosticiran-koronavirus-prvi-slucaj-zaraze-u-buzimu-543411 |website=www.oslobodjenje.ba |accessdate=27 March 2020 |language=bs-ba}}</ref> [[Cazin]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Iz Kantonalne bolnice Biha\u0107 potvrdili jedan slu\u010daj zaraze koronavirusom u Cazinu |url=https://www.cazin.net/vijesti/iz-kantonalne-bolnice-bihac-potvrdili-jedan-slucaj-zaraze-koronavirusom-u-cazinu |website=Cazin.NET |accessdate=30 March 2020 |language=en}}</ref>, [[Velika Kladu\u0161a]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.radiovkladusa.ba/prvi-slucaj-oboljelog-od-koronavirusa-registrovan-u-velikoj-kladusi/|title=Prvi slu\u010daj oboljelog od koronavirusa registrovan u Velikoj Kladu\u0161i|date=2020-03-31|website=Radio Velika Kladu\u0161a|language=bs-BA|access-date=2020-04-01}}</ref>\n| align=\"right\"| 20\n| align=\"right\"| 2\n| align=\"right\"| 0\n|-\n| align=\"left\" style=\"background:#EAECF0\"| [[West Herzegovina Canton]]\n| align=\"left\"| [[Grude]],<ref>{{cite web |title=Prvi slu\u010daj koronavirusa u Grudama: Zara\u017eeni mu\u0161karac ima te\u0161ku upalu plu\u0107a |url=https://www.dnevnik.ba/vijesti/prvi-slucaj-koronavirusa-u-grudama-zarazeni-muskarac-ima-tesku-upalu-pluca |website=Dnevnik.ba |accessdate=26 March 2020 |language=hr |date=25 March 2020}}</ref> [[Posu\u0161je]],<ref>{{cite web |title=Prvi slu\u010daj koronavirusa registrovan u Posu\u0161ju, zara\u017eena 33-godi\u0161njakinja |url=https://www.klix.ba/vijesti/bih/prvi-slucaj-koronavirusa-registrovan-u-posusju-zarazena-33-godisnjakinja/200328150 |website=Klix.ba |accessdate=28 March 2020 |language=bs-BA}}</ref> [[\u0160iroki Brijeg]]<ref>{{cite web |title=U \u0160irokom Brijegu potvr\u0111en prvi slu\u010daj koronavirusa, ukupno 137 u BiH |url=https://www.klix.ba/vijesti/bih/u-sirokom-brijegu-potvrdjen-prvi-slucaj-koronavirusa-ukupno-137-u-bih/200324010 |website=Klix.b